author: COMSOL
description: This tutorial model illustrates how to calculate the pressure drop and initial flow rate in a pipe system connected to water tank. The Pipe Flow Module contains ready to use friction models accounting for the surface roughness of pipes as well as pressure losses in bends and valves.
